text: Trypetoptera is a genus of marsh flies in the family Sciomyzidae. There are at least two described species in Trypetoptera. ==Species== *T. canadensis (Macquart, 1843) *T. punctulata (Scopoli, 1763) ==References== ==Further reading== * * * ==External links== * Category:Sciomyzidae
title: Trypetoptera
